    {
      "ingredient_lines": [],
      "instruction": "Heat up the leftover oil first and get the pan hot. Put ground beef and chopped onions into the pan, season, then cook until browned. Turn down the heat to low and add crushed tomatoes, salt/pepper/sugar, oregano, hot pepper flakes, and olive oil as needed. Stir and taste for any adjustments. I added a touch of balsamic towards the end to spice it up."
